      "title": "Woman injured in gun blast",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vavuniya - A woman has been admitted to the Vavuniya hospital after she was injured in a bomb explosion in Echankulam Salamban area yesterday morning.",
        "A 32-year-old woman from Vavunia-Kalmaduva area has been injured.",
        "The woman was gathering firewood in the forest area behind her house when a trap used for hunting animals exploded."
